SQL Assignments – Day 3 @DataBricks training

Introduction

These assignments helped me improve my understanding of SQL concepts from basic joins to advanced analytical queries.

The assignments covered important database topics such as:

- SQL Joins
- LEFT JOIN
- RIGHT JOIN
- FULL OUTER JOIN
- CROSS JOIN
- Window Functions
- ROW_NUMBER()
- RANK()
- DENSE_RANK()
- PARTITION BY
- LAG() and LEAD()
